{"id":108199,"title":"13 | 技术中台到底讲什么？","content":"","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":194577,"user_name":"soong","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1049954,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E3BECF2088F3D9","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/05/62/0a4e5831.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1585069134,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":74363,"content":"中台可以有不同的视角，在业务方和管理层的视角中，中台是一个偏向业务和组织的概念。在架构师和技术人员眼中，中台偏技术平台。不管何种视角，中台的本质是业务&#47;组织或技术能力的模块化和复用，最终目标是业务的规模化发展。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1585233143,"ip_address":"","comment_id":194577,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100031401,"comment_content":"关于中台，老师也提到了中台的缘起，其实就个人观点来看，我更倾向于认为是一种业务的组织形态！也不知道从什么时候开始，中台开始更多地出现在技术架构的讨论中，从一个偏业务的概念变得更偏技术！用技术推动中台化，本是好事，只是目前多数流于概念，流于炒作！不知道老师对此有什么看法？","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":488850,"discussion_content":"中台可以有不同的视角，在业务方和管理层的视角中，中台是一个偏向业务和组织的概念。在架构师和技术人员眼中，中台偏技术平台。不管何种视角，中台的本质是业务/组织或技术能力的模块化和复用，最终目标是业务的规模化发展。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1585233143,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":114707,"user_name":"古德","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1037755,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E3F646BB73F60E","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/d5/bb/98b93862.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1563368009,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":41964,"content":"是的，业务中台边界和划分不容易把控，而且随业务和团队会一直变化，这就是需要引入业务架构师和他们的价值所在，根据企业上下文和业务发展需要，不断调整业务中台的边界和划分，尽可能将企业业务能力抽象封装模块化和重用，提升研发效能，赋能业务创新。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1563454880,"ip_address":"","comment_id":114707,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100031401,"comment_content":"技术状态还比较容易划分和理解，但业务中台感觉很多时候边界就比较难界定，如果只是抽取通用功能部分，很多时候内容其实不多；如果过多的把业务纳入中台，这样又不够抽象，和具体业务耦合度太高","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":458788,"discussion_content":"是的，业务中台边界和划分不容易把控，而且随业务和团队会一直变化，这就是需要引入业务架构师和他们的价值所在，根据企业上下文和业务发展需要，不断调整业务中台的边界和划分，尽可能将企业业务能力抽象封装模块化和重用，提升研发效能，赋能业务创新。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1563454880,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":256867,"user_name":"Paul","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1050294,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7018DE791BBAE7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/06/b6/4db00076.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1603768844,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":93908,"content":"有本质区别，中台更多是一个组织和业务的概念，技术架构在其次。\n\n你简单可以这样理解，我们编程经历了面向过程 -&gt; 面向对象 -&gt; 面向组件 -&gt; 面向服务 -&gt; 面向平台(中台)的过程。\n\n普通程序关注过程&#47;对象&#47;组件这些底层抽象层次。\n\n架构师关注服务这个中间抽象层次。\n\n但是在技术&#47;业务总监或者CTO的眼中，他们关注中台-把业务能力+团队作为一个重用单位，利用中台去支持业务的迭代和创新，是更高维度的抽象。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1604242600,"ip_address":"","comment_id":256867,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100031401,"comment_content":"图中怎么没有后台了？感觉图中的业务中台就是之前的后台，技术中台就是之前的服务器、数据库之类的东西；所谓的中台就是把以前的后台改个名？两者有什么具体区别呢？","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":508147,"discussion_content":"有本质区别，中台更多是一个组织和业务的概念，技术架构在其次。\n\n你简单可以这样理解，我们编程经历了面向过程 -&amp;gt; 面向对象 -&amp;gt; 面向组件 -&amp;gt; 面向服务 -&amp;gt; 面向平台(中台)的过程。\n\n普通程序关注过程/对象/组件这些底层抽象层次。\n\n架构师关注服务这个中间抽象层次。\n\n但是在技术/业务总监或者CTO的眼中，他们关注中台-把业务能力+团队作为一个重用单位，利用中台去支持业务的迭代和创新，是更高维度的抽象。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1604242600,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":123618,"user_name":"草上飞蝶号🙈","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1604231,"ip_address":"","ucode":"DF06A06BE61317","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/7a/87/668a4f38.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1565713712,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":45460,"content":"技术中台主要是企业管理层和架构师，需要理解和掌握，对于一般开发人员，简单了解即可。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1565789368,"ip_address":"","comment_id":123618,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100031401,"comment_content":"老师的层次有点高哦，作为初级开发者来说有点难啊","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":462748,"discussion_content":"技术中台主要是企业管理层和架构师，需要理解和掌握，对于一般开发人员，简单了解即可。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1565789368,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":122158,"user_name":"小太阳","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1566413,"ip_address":"","ucode":"80FD4A871ABFAD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/e6/cd/bf5e928c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1565312281,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":44939,"content":"如果是企业新系统，没有遗留系统负担，PaaS可以一步到位考虑Kubernetes平台(如果企业研发资源和能力一般，建议不要自建而是采用云服务，例如阿里云k8s)，k8s已经覆盖了服务发现，应用配置，容器调度和部署，自愈和自动伸缩，资源隔离和配额，分布式存储，分布式任务等微服务基本关注点，再配合一些其它一些中间件(网关，oauth2，消息，限流，分布式数据访问层，日志&#47;调用链&#47;metrics监控和告警，其中部分中间件和开源产品可以参考我之前课程《微服务架构实践160讲》），即可搭建一套比较前卫的PaaS平台。当然，企业实际PaaS平台的构建不是一蹴而就，需要长期的投入、运维、迭代和优化。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1565364305,"ip_address":"","comment_id":122158,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100031401,"comment_content":"技术中台中paas层如何提炼呢？这涉及到业务中台技术选型的问题。感觉进入了先有鸡还是先有蛋的轮回。如果是这样，paas这块有初始推荐么？又如何迭代优化呢？","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":462125,"discussion_content":"如果是企业新系统，没有遗留系统负担，PaaS可以一步到位考虑Kubernetes平台(如果企业研发资源和能力一般，建议不要自建而是采用云服务，例如阿里云k8s)，k8s已经覆盖了服务发现，应用配置，容器调度和部署，自愈和自动伸缩，资源隔离和配额，分布式存储，分布式任务等微服务基本关注点，再配合一些其它一些中间件(网关，oauth2，消息，限流，分布式数据访问层，日志/调用链/metrics监控和告警，其中部分中间件和开源产品可以参考我之前课程《微服务架构实践160讲》），即可搭建一套比较前卫的PaaS平台。当然，企业实际PaaS平台的构建不是一蹴而就，需要长期的投入、运维、迭代和优化。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1565364305,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":114461,"user_name":"而立斋","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1087258,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5FED6E9E148195","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/97/1a/389eab84.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1563322304,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":41841,"content":"中台也是模块化和平台化思想，不光是技术架构，还有组织甚至业务也可以模块化和平台化，理解思想即可，没必要太纠结术语。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1563363939,"ip_address":"","comment_id":114461,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100031401,"comment_content":"我理解的中台跟平台化差不多，但总是区分不出来","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":458674,"discussion_content":"中台也是模块化和平台化思想，不光是技术架构，还有组织甚至业务也可以模块化和平台化，理解思想即可，没必要太纠结术语。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1563363939,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":137366,"user_name":"云淡风清","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1111751,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5CAA72D6A9E89F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/f6/c7/18ddb896.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1569724444,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":52838,"content":"用户管理和登录认证的功能可以做在一起，也可以分开，各有利弊，具体要看